body:
Hey guys, for today's video I decided to record a game of the walls with some cool peeps on TS (Tel, D00ZiE, MissCarmel and Glitchy).  I hope you enjoy!

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HLbAYW_1Oz8&feature=youtu.be

EDIT:  If you're wondering why the left side of the screen is blurred out most of the time, it's to block out player reports c:
